<HEAD>List of Winners For The Annual Awards for Cable Excellence</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here is the list of winners for the Awards for
Cable Excellence, or ACE awards, honoring outstanding achievement in
cable television programming.
   1. DRAMATIC SERIES: ``Vietnam War Story'' Home Box Office.
